<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">中央银行</span>大洋洲</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">澳大利亚：<a href="/item/%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C" target="_blank">澳大利亚储备银行</a>（The Reserve Bank of Australia）<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":14," data-sup="14">
[14]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[14]_79768"> </a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">巴布亚新几内亚：<a href="/item/%E5%B7%B4%E5%B8%83%E4%BA%9A%E6%96%B0%E5%87%A0%E5%86%85%E4%BA%9A%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C" target="_blank">巴布亚新几内亚银行</a>（The Bank of Papua New Guinea）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">斐济：<a href="/item/%E6%96%90%E6%B5%8E%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C" target="_blank">斐济储备银行</a>（The Reserve Bank of Fiji）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">基里巴斯：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">库克群岛：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">马绍尔群岛：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">密克罗尼西亚联邦：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">瑙鲁：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">纽埃：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">帕劳：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">萨摩亚：<a href="/item/%E8%90%A8%E6%91%A9%E4%BA%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C" target="_blank">萨摩亚中央银行</a>（The Central Bank of Samoa）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">所罗门群岛：所罗门群岛中央银行（The Central Bank of Solomon Islands）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">汤加：<a href="/item/%E6%B1%A4%E5%8A%A0%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C" target="_blank">汤加国家储备银行</a>（The National Reserve Bank of Tonga）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">图瓦卢：无中央银行</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">瓦努阿图：<a href="/item/%E7%93%A6%E5%8A%AA%E9%98%BF%E5%9B%BE%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C" target="_blank">瓦努阿图储备银行</a>（The Reserve Bank of Vanuatu）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">新西兰：<a href="/item/%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E5%85%B0%E5%82%A8%E5%A4%87%E9%93%B6%E8%A1%8C" target="_blank">新西兰储备银行</a>（The Reserve Bank of New Zealand）<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":15," data-sup="15">
[15]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[15]_79768"> </a>
</div>
